 preference ("},{"code":"calledLaunchIsSuppressed","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":") and number of snapshot metrics, specifically:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"header":"row","rows":[[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Key"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Value Description","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"calledLaunchIsSuppressed"}]}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When "},{"code":"true","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", prevents the application’s GUI from appearing whenever the app is called by an explicitly defined caller (","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"--caller"},{"type":"text","text":"), "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"unless"}]},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"com.bcg.biometry.reminder.agent.<UUID>"},{"type":"text","text":" is the caller. "},{"code":"True","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" if the end-user has explicitly 1) scheduled or 2) declined reminders. If "},{"code":"true","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" because the end-user has scheduled a reminder, accompanied by an "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.bcg.biometry\/documentation\/BCGBiometry\/AppState","type":"reference"},{"text":" of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"pendingUserScheduledReminder"},{"type":"text","text":". If "},{"code":"true","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" because the end-user has declined reminders, accompanied by an ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.bcg.biometry\/documentation\/BCGBiometry\/AppState","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" of "},{"code":"declined","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"appState"}]}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Most recent state of the application. Possible states listed in the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.bcg.biometry\/documentation\/BCGBiometry\/AppState"},{"text":" enum. ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"WARNING:"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" Do not key actions or control flow based on "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"appState"},{"type":"text","text":" because race conditions can exist – "},{"code":"appState","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" must be used for reporting purposes only.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"cliLaunchCount","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Running total of times the BCGBiometry CLI has been launched"}]}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"guiLaunchCount"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Running total of times the BCGBiometry GUI has been launched"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"guiLaunchCountUntilEnabled","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Running total of times the BCGBiometry GUI was launched until biometry was enabled","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"launchAgentName","type":"text"}]}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Name of the launch agent for the upcoming or most recent reminder (ex: "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"com.bcg.biometry.reminder.agent.<UUID>"},{"type":"text","text":")"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"reminderSetDate","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Date and time of setting the upcoming or most recent reminder","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"reminderGetDate"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Date and time of getting the upcoming or most recent reminder","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"reminderSetToGetDateCalendarDaysUTC"}]}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The difference in calendar days between "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"reminderSetDate"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"reminderGetDate"},{"type":"text","text":", determined by summing the number of UTC midnights that have elapsed from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"reminderSetDate"},{"text":" to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"reminderGetDate"},{"text":". This count disregards specific times of the day and solely reflects dates in terms of count of elapsed UTC midnights.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"reminderCount","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Running total of end-user scheduled reminders. This counter is incremented when the end-user clicks the “Remind Me Later” button and selects a date and time to be reminded."}]}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"dismissalCount","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Running total of dismissals. This counter is incremented when the end-user clicks the “Dismiss” button.","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"declinationCount"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Running total of declinations. This counter is incremented (and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"calledLaunchIsSuppressed"},{"text":" is set to true) when the end-user selects a declination reason after clicking the “Don’t Remind Me” button. Generally, should be 0 if never declined or 1 if declined; however, values greater than 1 indicate the end-user declined and either 1) subsequently launched the app by double-clicking on it the Applications folder or 2) the intervaled launcher (such as ","type":"text"},{"code":"jamf","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":") was configured to not pass a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"--caller"},{"type":"text","text":", triggering "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"BCGBiometry"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" to ignore the ","type":"text"},{"code":"calledLaunchIsSuppressed","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" value, which, is set to true when declining reminders (bypassing the called-launch suppression feature)."}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"declinationDate"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Date and time of the most recent declination.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"declinationReason"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Reason of the most recent declination. Possible reasons listed in the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.bcg.biometry\/documentation\/BCGBiometry\/DeclinationReason","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" enumeration."}]}]]],"type":"table"},{"text":"Application Interfaces","type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Application-Interfaces"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The application provides a Graphical User Interface (GUI) and a Command Line Interface (CLI), but does "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"not"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" provide an Application Programming Interface (API) other than its own internal private classes and structs.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The Graphical User Interface (GUI) application is an ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"accessory"}]},{"type":"text","text":" application, which, means the app does not have a dock icon or menubar (with the exception of an optional but unused icon in the system menubar)."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is not desirable for "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"BCGBiometry","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" to have a dock icon because it would appear whenever using the application’s Command Line Interface (CLI) (possibly being perceived as an icon “randomly” appearing and disappearing in users’ docks).","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"It is also not desirable for ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"BCGBiometry","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" to have a menubar, because – by default – the menubar would have a “Quit” button that would allow users to bypass the desired workflow of either 1) enabling biometry, 2) scheduling a reminder or 3) declining reminders before quitting the application."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"BCGBiometry","type":"text"}]},{"text":"‘s election to be an ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"accessory","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" is reflected in the app bundle’s ","type":"text"},{"code":"Info.plist","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" as the "},{"code":"LSUIElement","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" being set to "},{"code":"1","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Graphical User Interface","level":4,"type":"heading","anchor":"Graphical-User-Interface"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The Graphical User Interface (GUI) may be launched by double-clicking on the app icon or programatically by a caller, such as a reminder agent or the jamf daemon.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"To launch the GUI as a caller, provide the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"--caller"},{"text":" flag and provide a name for the caller (eg: ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"--caller <someCallerName>"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Providing a ","type":"text"},{"code":"--caller","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" value to ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"BCGBiometry"}]},{"type":"text","text":" lets it know how to handle the request."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"When the reminder agent launches the application, it lets ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"BCGBiometry"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" know that the reminder agent is the caller by specifying itself as the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"--caller"},{"type":"text","text":" when launching the application:"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"\/Applications\/BCGBiometry.app --caller com.bcg.biometry.reminder.agent.<UUID>"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the "},{"code":"--caller","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"com.bcg.biometry.reminder.agent.<UUID>"},{"type":"text","text":", Called-Launch Suppression ("},{"code":"calledLaunchIsSuppressed","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":") is ignored because that reminder would have been explicitly requested and scheduled by the end-user – and should be displayed regardless."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"However, if the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"--caller"},{"text":" is anything else (like ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"jamf"},{"text":"), Called-Launch Suppression is respected (If ","type":"text"},{"code":"calledLaunchIsSuppressed","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"true"},{"text":" and the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"--caller"},{"text":" is ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"not","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"com.bcg.biometry.reminder.agent.<UUID>"},{"type":"text","text":", then the app will "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"not"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" launch)."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":4,"text":"Command Line Interface","anchor":"Command-Line-Interface","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The Command Line Interface (CLI) can provide biometry status of the Mac.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To get the biometry status of the Mac, run:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"\/Applications\/BCGBiometry.app\/Contents\/MacOS\/BCGBiometry --get biometry"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If biometry is not enabled, ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"none"},{"text":" is returned. ","type":"text"},{"text":"\n","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"If TouchID is enabled, "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"touchID"},{"type":"text","text":" is returned. "},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"text":"If FaceID is enabled, ","type":"text"},{"code":"faceID","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is returned ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"(on some future hypothetical Mac that supports FaceID)"}]},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"level":3,"anchor":"Packaging","text":"Packaging","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Archive, Notarize and Export the app bundle to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"\/Applications\/BCGBiometry.app"},{"type":"text","text":" and build a signed package using the productbuilt command:"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"productbuild --sign \"Developer ID Installer: The Boston Consulting Group International GmbH (GRML9N57WB)\" --component \/Applications\/BCGBiometry.app \/Users\/Shared\/BCGBiometry_YYYYMMDD.pkg"}]}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/bcgbiometry"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[[]]},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"metadata":{"externalID":"BCGBiometry","roleHeading":"Application","title":"BCGBiometry","images":[{"identifier":"1-BCGBiometryIcon.png","type":"icon"}],"role":"collection","modules":[{"name":"BCGBiometry"}],"symbolKind":"module"},"references":{"doc://com.bcg.biometry/documentation/BCGBiometry/D